title: Ranked Was Just Reset
body: Did I miss something? Is it the new season or is it on purpose? Is it cause of the maintenance?

replies.body: It's because of maintenance!  It's just a display issue on your profile and everything will be restored after it's over!  Updates will be posted on the [service status](http://status.leagueoflegends.com/#na) page.  Hope that gives some relief!
it is fixed now, just restart your client
it should return to normal when riot is done with maintance
